  "detailed_description": "War Maze is turn-based strategy game based on chess!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/558cce1d05f62f9f3fca05a42b7a1cce.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br>War Maze matches are played on a map of tiles, similar to chess. Each piece has different tile-based movement and attack patterns. Each piece also has a certain amount of attack and health points.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/4c0e716682fdc44f019af35499fb1207.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br>Beat your way through the campaign to get a sense of each piece's mechanics and unlock skins!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/61a7496b2e5191c08fab26c398aa3390.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br>Buy and select skins to form your own army to fight with in multiplayer mode!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/9e6eb948740f838107552f110d7e75bc.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/3ee3cd5af3030a67e8a41b4709986546.avif?t=1707583109\" width=374 height=448 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "War Maze is turn-based strategy game based on chess!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/558cce1d05f62f9f3fca05a42b7a1cce.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br>War Maze matches are played on a map of tiles, similar to chess. Each piece has different tile-based movement and attack patterns. Each piece also has a certain amount of attack and health points.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/4c0e716682fdc44f019af35499fb1207.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br>Beat your way through the campaign to get a sense of each piece's mechanics and unlock skins!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/61a7496b2e5191c08fab26c398aa3390.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br>Buy and select skins to form your own army to fight with in multiplayer mode!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/9e6eb948740f838107552f110d7e75bc.avif?t=1707583109\" width=572 height=282 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2585570/extras/3ee3cd5af3030a67e8a41b4709986546.avif?t=1707583109\" width=374 height=448 /></span>",
